sub_title: Program Manager at Nyenrode Business University
summary:
I am a project manager with more than 10 years of working experience in different international environments. I worked in public and private sector, higher education and media & communication.

I am passionate about intercultural communication, engaging with people and project management. I fluently speak English, Spanish, Slovene and actively improving Dutch. I have lived and worked in Slovenia, USA, Spain and now in the Netherlands. I have a great customer service attitude and I am used of working with diverse international teams. I am passionate about managing and engaging with projects that improve our society and aim to plan for a better more sustainable and inclusive world for all.
